{"tid":1801811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英建議要求審計署削減港台經費","createTime":"2019-12-29T03:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T03:07:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c1f34fd145f779c09c21f1e3c08055e370af7b7","tid":1801811,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:05:14.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席、前行政長官梁振英在社交網站貼文，建議政府不如要求審計署全面審查香港電台帳目，衡工量值，以今天網台林立，香港人只有750萬乘24小時的接收新聞資訊和娛樂節目為前提，了解有沒有空間削減港台經費。<br />\n<br />\n20多位香港電台節目顧問團成員，日前去信商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華，表示留意到香港電台節目製作人員工會表示，港台新聞部因報道反修例運動花費大增，超出年度預算約500萬元，因而要扣減人手，相反警隊過去半年逾時工作津貼開支共約9億5000萬元。信中指，同樣是為市民服務，港台員工待遇差天共地，要求當局為港台增撥資源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500001-20191229.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500001-20191229.htm&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=b0cfb754\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500001-20191229.htm&h=4fca07fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500001-20191229.htm</a>"},{"pid":"70c261c2b29af752909b9eb5b6b06303fbb2feb8","tid":1801811,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e49b6f8dc64f24ca7b338d974ca5ec4c2c355f20","tid":1801811,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"呢件廢老仲喺度攝政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d85879391328fa12ede91f0245310da99f8310d","tid":1801811,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"要cut就Cut咗梁振英啲津貼先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}